Package samples.commui

Interface Summary
AsyncCommandListener Callback interface for receiving results of SNAP commands.
ButtonListListener Listener class for button press actions
MainApp Interface to be implemented by MIDlets that wish to make use of the Community functionality.
 

Class Summary
Buddy Buddy class for chat functionality.
BuddyList Implements the list of Buddies and their presence and chat status.
BuddyView This class implements all Buddy related UI components and layouts.
ButtonListView Class to define the layout of the Button List
Cell This class represents the smallest defined element in a maze.
Chat This class implements chat window functionality
CommUITest CommUI Main Test Midlet
Community Main manager class for MazeRacer sample game functionality.
CommunityView Superclass of all Views.
Dialog Implements a full-screen multi-line text or data input dialog, with configurable softkeys (labels and targets.)
EmailDobView EmailDobView is a screen for capturing a user's email address and date of birth for new account creation.
LoginView Main screen of the Community LoginView of the Community package.
Maze This class represents a two-dimensional maze.
MazeRacer This class implements the maze racer game engine
MazeRacerView This class implements visualization for the maze racer game.
Player This class represents a player in the sample game.
RankingView This class implements all Rankings related UI components and layout.
SectionNavigator Class to implement all Navigation components:left and right arrow
SplashView This class implements a splash screen/image to display the Game image or the Message of the Day extends CommunityView
TermsView This screen shows SNAP terms-and-conditions text and waits for user's acceptance and/or rejection of the terms.
TextView Class that implements all text related GUI component layout.
UserPassView UserPassView is a screen for capturing a user's username and password for new account creation.
Util Utility class that implements math functions:Random
